author: @Alex4n3r
text: First layer is ReLu, not dense layer. It won't even be a straight line as one can check for negative x. You can also see: sgd is much better than adam with much less epochs. Chart.js doesn't give a damn about canvas size. Use chart options responsive:false, maintainAspectRation:false to fix that. By the way:  doctype is missing ;) Seems like the html-pope will excommunicate you!
